title: Rick Ross Interview
itunes:title: Rick Ross Interview
description:
Rick Ross stops by the Breakfast Club to talk about his book "Hurricanes". He talks about some stories in the book as well as discusses his album, "Port of Miami 2". Ross also reacts to Nicki Minaj calling him out on Joe Budden's podcast. Todays Donkey of the day goes to Connor McGregor for punching a bar patron over a whiskey dispute and Angela Yee helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
